               stealing a Silver Tankard, value 7 Pounds, the Goods of 
                     <persName id="t17420224-1-victim31" type="victimName">
                        Hearsay 
                        Broomhead 
                     <interp inst="t17420224-1-victim31" type="surname" value="Broomhead"></interp>
