            . I have known him seven or eight Years, and never heard any Ill of him, or knew him to be guilty of any Crime: I was a Neighbour to him.</p>
               <p>The Jury <rs id="t17420224-1-verdict4" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17420224-1-verdict4" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17420224-1-verdict4" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               acquitted the Prisoner of the stealing out of the Dwelling House, and found him guilty of simple Felony.
            </rs>
